\pard\f0\fs28    {\b 4. A. porsildii} Elis. Ekman,{\i  Svensk Bot. Tidskr.}{\b  21}: 51 (1927). Like {\b 3} but not more than 10 cm; basal leaves more or less glabrous on both surfaces but flowering stems and cauline leaves somewhat tomentose. 2n = 63, 70.{\i  Damp mountain heaths. N.W. Fennoscandia.} Fe No Su.
\par 
